data.description: Beautifully updated single-level home is ready for new owners! Newer flooring throughout, new roof in 2019, new furnace in 2020, updated plumbing in 2022, updated windows, and newer water heater. Covered carport on front as well as a large 2 car garage/shop in back! RV parking off the alley access. Fenced backyard with garden space and many fruit trees for your enjoyment.
